gend Boats, thank you for coming to see us at the Toronto International Boat Show.</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Yours in Boating,</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">{!Opportunity.OwnerFullName}</font></div><div><font face="arial">{!Opportunity.OwnerTitle}</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial" size="2">{!Opportunity.OwnerEmail}</font></div><div><font face="arial" size="2">{!Opportunity.OwnerPhone}</font></div><div><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial" size="2">www.legendboats.com</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div>]]></td>
